      <title>美联储逆回购工具余额跌至 1000 亿美元以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/fed-reverse-repo-facility-balances-sink-below-100-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，在政策制定者调整参数后，投资者存放在主要美联储设施的资金量自 2021 年以来首次跌破 1000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/fed-reverse-repo-facility-balances-sink-below-100-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 18:39:00 GMT</pubDate>
