      <title>黑石集团邀请 KKR 和 Ares 的交易员推动私人信贷业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/blackstone-taps-dealmakers-from-kkr-ares-in-private-credit-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的另类资产管理公司黑石集团 (Blackstone Inc.) 正在继续向私人信贷领域扩张，目前该公司正在招聘两名信贷资深人士来负责投资级交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/blackstone-taps-dealmakers-from-kkr-ares-in-private-credit-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 18:23:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
